{"tid":1855461,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"支共電訊唔係人 （鐘移)","createTime":"2020-02-01T05:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T09:01:32.000Z","uid":74821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"734372969b2c5d11ed4a0e4d6a5811984154845d","tid":1855461,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"現時疫情嚴峻市道低迷 ，當其他電訊公司出晒email，擔心員工受到疫情風險而提早收舖，唯有支共鐘移電訊門市新任腦細，為咗做靚條數，完全唔理同事安危，唔提早閂門都算啦，仲要加長營業時間，唔到數要留堂，延長工作時間，間爛鬼公司，咩防疫物資都唔提供，叫啲員工周街撲，仲邊有時間同你跑數呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲有行入呢間公司好多都係唔識帶口罩嘅藍c，同國內嘅尊貴同胞，我哋比起其他公司遇到嘅風險更大，大佬，我打份工架咋唔係搵條命同你博!<br />\n<br />\n利申: 代po"},{"pid":"71b986abe5de6ca566d2f769fa73ca6675f4abbb","tid":1855461,"uid":144212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"今日有口罩返呀。不過薄左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a4276bb3ab8bd36af2fe625b9156fcc06b52f0","tid":1855461,"uid":29238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"認住邊個落order返工  有咩事就同佢深情一吻"},{"pid":"3f4368c386037f74f5c77757836befe2c9dd89ed","tid":1855461,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"最緊要大家唔好幫襯"},{"pid":"dbf272bd9fed37283a8654877f232ccd190c0d00","tid":1855461,"uid":172157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"當門市香港人係狗，office辦大陸佬係home office<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d230d8522e709800babe3c8d62600d722d218a4","tid":1855461,"uid":9743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"以我所知c記都係咁,話就話營業時間改做12-8,但其實逼自己d員工繼續留鋪打call搵生意,香港商家佬都唔好得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39f09a1bf1967c2d7380e2f353197aa82d3e257","tid":1855461,"uid":98479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:24:18.000Z","ms